Title: Youth to work or studies
Description: This document is a funding application to the European Social Fund. It includes a background to and description of the intervention. It also comprises information about the setting, actors involved and expected outcomes.

Title: The one withdrawing, youth sitting at home
Description: This document is a project proposal that encompass a description of the problem, the intervention and its intended implementation, the youth, the aims and objectives as well as an overview of the collaborating partners.

Title: Application regarding funds for social investments
Description: This document is a funding application to the local municipal social investment fund. It includes a short summary of the idea as well as a description of the problem, the aims, the objectives, the intervention and its intended implementation, the youth and the plans for evaluation.
